    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of the species Betula nigra, often used in the making of small turned articles, such as clothes pins and toys.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
